description:
So I was walking around in the old town of Marbella and a woman looked mad at me and called me estupida ... So with my “stupid head” I thought it was probably because I didn’t wear a mask.. So I asked her in English why she was mad. Her response was that I just want to be “pretty” and because of my selfishness I’m killing people ...🙄So I looked around ... and told her that I didn’t see any dead bodies ... Did she? Her response was you know what I mean.... And of course I told her no I don’t .... If your mask works ... then why in godsname should you be afraid??? The end!!! She looked pissed... shook her head and walked away .... Why don’t they ever have a good argument??? 😂🤣#masksareforidiots
